The GPU Age
-----------

The challenge for Nvidia is that this future isn=E2=80=99t particularly inv=
estable; indeed, the idea assumes a capacity overhang at some point, which =
is not great for the stock price! That, though, is how technology advances,=
 and even if a cliff eventually comes, there is a lot of money to be made i=
n the meantime.

That noted, the biggest short-term question I have is around Nvidia CEO Jen=
sen Huang=E2=80=99s insistence that the current wave of demand is in fact t=
he dawn of what he calls accelerated computing; from the Nvidia earnings ca=
ll ( https://seekingalpha.com/article/4630703-nvidia-corp-nvda-q2-2024-earn=
ings-call-transcript ) :

I=E2=80=99m reluctant to guess about the future and so I=E2=80=99ll answer =
the question from the first principle of computer science perspective. It i=
