And so I think the data centers around the world recognize this, that this =
is the best way to deploy resources, deploy capital going forward for data =
centers. This is true for the world=E2=80=99s clouds and you=E2=80=99re see=
ing a whole crop of new GPU-specialized cloud service providers. One of the=
